HEADWORD: Grammaticaster
<hw>Gram*mat"icas"ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[LL.]</ety>
<def>A petty grammarian; a grammatical pedant or pretender.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>My noble Neophite, my little <qex>grammaticaster</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>B. Jonson.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grammatication</ent>⟦br⟧
